data.description: Click the Virtual Tour link to view the 3D walkthrough    Prime Location Meets Exquisite Living!  Welcome to 9403 Somers Bend, nestled in the coveted Somerset Trails community of San Antonio, TX. This stunning two-story residence offers all the comforts of modern living while boasting prime accessibility features. With its strategic location off I-35 and Somerset Road, the commute to Randolph Air Force Base or the vibrant Downtown San Antonio is a sheer delight, ensuring less time on the road and more time at home.    Property Highlights:    Dimensions: Generously spread over two levels, this home presents 3 spacious bedrooms, 2.5 luxurious baths, and a convenient 2-car garage.  Entertainer's Delight: The first floor is tailor-made for hosting with a seamless flow from the kitchen to the living and dining areas. Whether it's a cozy family dinner or a grand gathering, this space is designed to cater to all.  Gourmet Kitchen: A chef's dream comes true with 42-inch cabinetry, sleek granite countertops, and a large central island - making both meal prep and conversations a pleasure.  Upstairs Oasis: The second floor offers a well-thought-out split floor plan, ensuring privacy for all bedrooms. It's perfect for those who cherish their personal space.  Primary Suite: A true haven! The primary bedroom comes with an attached garden tub/shower combo, perfect for unwinding after a long day. Not to mention the Texas-sized walk-in closet that answers all your storage prayers.  Outdoor Living: Step out to the covered patio, an ideal spot for your morning coffee or evening barbecues. Feel the breeze, take in the views, and make countless memories!  This gem of a property combines elegance, convenience, and a prime location to offer an unparalleled living experience.
